data.name: GoogleCalendar - SmpRip
data.description:
ATTENTION!!!
This Script is OUTDATED and discontinued!!!
==================================================

Just one more style for Google's Calendar, my 1st to this site/webapp...

With this style my aim was maintain the original look and feel of Google Calendar and try to rip some unnecessary spaces!
It was tested with English (US) and partialy with Portuguese (PT) languages.

--- Screens was taken with (v0.750) ---

data.name: Gmail Chat - NtmWay
data.description:
ATTENTION!!!
This Script is OUTDATED and discontinued!!!
==================================================

A complete remake of my old style, now works with and without "Pictures in chat" (by Dave C) Gmail LAB!

--- Screens taken with (v1.000) ---
The screens have no paint tricks at all, they are simple and plain direct screens, i only mount 4-in-1 for simplify the comparison.

data.name: Google - New TopNavBar - Ntm Style
data.description:
ATTENTION!!!
This Script is OUTDATED and discontinued!!!
==================================================

I made this Script with 2 points in my mind...
- 1st = As a complement for various of my other scripts where i had this very same code.
- 2nd = Try to put the newest Google top nav bar much more smaller in all the places where it appears.

Notes:
The 1st point it will be 100% satisfied in time!
The 2nd point i can't verify with 100% certain... If your domain is not covered please report-it to me in the discussions and i will try to add it in the next update.

--- Screens taken with (v0.100) ---
